Title: The Ballad of Kenneth Parcell
Plot: Liz looks for a new best friend after discovering that Jenna has traded their friendship for fame. Tracy contemplates mortality as Dotcom and Grizz scramble to show him that life is still worth living. Meanwhile, Jack decides to end the page program in order to impress Hank Hooper.
GuestStars: Ken Howard, Andy Samberg, Emma Stone, Nick Cannon, Mick Foley, Julie Dretzin, Steve Earle
